397
00:25:46,629 --> 00:25:48,014
Eul Soon. Nejdeš von?

398
00:25:48,559 --> 00:25:51,055
Áno, mala by som.

399
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:53,311
Na čo myslím?

400
00:26:03,149 --> 00:26:04,221
