402
00:26:17,889 --> 00:26:19,616
(Chlapec, ktorý vidí duchov)

403
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:22,117
Bože, vysmievajú sa mi?

404
00:26:30,069 --> 00:26:33,372
Čo mi to robia? Dočerta.

405
00:26:35,980 --> 00:26:38,475
Daj si v noci tie okuliare dole.

406
00:26:40,579 --> 00:26:42,407
Hej, dedička trhu Biely tiger.

407
00:26:43,050 --> 00:26:44,737
Hej, to je dedič Knediel Eul.

408
00:26:46,690 --> 00:26:49,184
Hej. Môžem sa tiež napiť?

409
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:57,613
